  "description": {
    "zh": "你好啊, 终于联系到你了佣兵。 我想我们可能还不认识, 不过人们都喊我叫 莲花 。我从这地区的一些本地商人和雇员兵那儿打听到你办事好像很靠谱? \n\n其实我一直想找个人合作, 但是要知道当今世道要了解一个人可靠可信是很重要的, 特别是像我这样的人, 毕竟在塔科夫这个地方生意至上。 你给表现, 我出报酬, 咱们双赢。 现在在有些当地土匪和人渣正盘踞在市区和郊区大煞风景, 扰乱地方安全。我想让你帮忙做掉他们。\n\n祝你好运, 保持联系。",
    "en": "Hello soldier. I don't think we know eachother yet, people refer to me as Lotus. Word got around in the region that you seem to be reliable, is that true?\n\nKnowing reliable and trustworthy people is important these days, especially for someone like me, after all business is everything here in Tarkov. How about you prove how reliable you are and if it is worth it to work with you, you will get some benefit from our work too so it's a win-win for both of us.\n\nA few local bandits and other scum have made a few local areas in and around town less safe than usual, I want you to get rid of a them.\n\nGood luck, we will stay in touch."
  },
